# Quarterly canon reviews

One file per review session: YYYY-Q*.md. Three questions:
- Is the rule still violated in the wild?
- Was the rule violated by someone who'd read it?
- Has a new pattern emerged?

See Step 5 of the lifecycle in
docs/canon-revisions/2026-05-19-plan-to-canon-process.md.

First quarterly review scheduled for 2026-08-19.

This folder also hosts the rolling progress doc for the language-patch
overhaul: 2026-language-patch-progress.md (created when batch 3
ships).
